Class TimeSeries

  • java.lang.Object
    • xstream.TimeSeries
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Externalizable, Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ReadableTimeSeries, WritableTimeSeries

    public abstract class TimeSeries
extends Object
implements Externalizable
    An abstract implementation of timeseries using partitioned time slots appropriate for storage and cluster computing framework.
